flowchart TD
    Start([User: Apply Filters/Search]) --> UserActions[User selects filters and search]
    UserActions --> Filters[User selects filters:<br/>Type, Status, Priority, Category, Tags, Date range]
    UserActions --> Search[User enters search: keyword]
    UserActions --> Sort[User selects sort: field, order]
    
    Filters --> UpdateFilterState[UI Component: Update Filter State]
    Search --> UpdateFilterState
    Sort --> UpdateFilterState
    
    UpdateFilterState --> UpdateLocal[Update local filter state]
    UpdateLocal --> Debounce[Debounce search input 300ms]
    Debounce --> BuildQuery[Build query parameters]
    
    BuildQuery --> UpdateStore[State Management: Update Filters]
    UpdateStore --> DispatchFilters[Dispatch: setFilters, setSearchQuery, setSortOptions]
    DispatchFilters --> StoreUpdate[Store: Update filter state]
    
    StoreUpdate --> CheckCache[React Query: Check Cache]
    CheckCache --> BuildCacheKey[Build cache key from filters/search/sort]
    BuildCacheKey --> CacheExists{Data exists in cache?}
    CacheExists -->|Found & Fresh| ReturnCached[Return cached data]
    CacheExists -->|Not found or Stale| FetchAPI[Fetch from API]
    
    ReturnCached --> RenderResults
    FetchAPI --> APIService[API Service: fetchGoals]
    APIService --> BuildQueryString[Build query string:<br/>?type=quantitative,binary<br/>&status=active<br/>&priority=high,medium<br/>&category=Health<br/>&tags=fitness<br/>&startDateFrom=2024-01-01<br/>&deadlineTo=2024-12-31<br/>&search=weight%20loss<br/>&sort=deadline<br/>&order=asc<br/>&page=1<br/>&limit=20]
    
    BuildQueryString --> HTTPRequest[HTTP Request: GET /api/goals]
    HTTPRequest --> Backend[Backend API Handler]
    Backend --> ParseQuery[Parse query parameters]
    ParseQuery --> BuildDBQuery[Build database query:<br/>WHERE clauses from filters<br/>Full-text search on title/description<br/>ORDER BY from sort options<br/>LIMIT/OFFSET from pagination]
    
    BuildDBQuery --> UseIndexes[Use indexes:<br/>Index on: type, status, priority<br/>Index on: category, tags<br/>Index on: deadline, createdAt<br/>Full-text index on: title, description]
    
    UseIndexes --> ExecuteQuery[Database: Execute Query]
    ExecuteQuery --> SQLQuery[SELECT goals WHERE ...<br/>AND title LIKE '%weight loss%'<br/>OR description LIKE '%weight loss%'<br/>ORDER BY deadline ASC<br/>LIMIT 20 OFFSET 0]
    
    SQLQuery --> ReturnResults[Return: Goals array + total count]
    ReturnResults --> APIResponse[API Response: 200 OK]
    APIResponse --> TransformResponse[API Service: Transform Response]
    TransformResponse --> ConvertDates[Convert dates]
    ConvertDates --> AddComputed[Add computed fields]
    
    AddComputed --> UpdateCache2[React Query: Update Cache]
    UpdateCache2 --> CacheResults[Cache results with key]
    CacheResults --> SetExpiration[Set cache expiration 5 minutes]
    
    SetExpiration --> UpdateStore2[State Management: Update Store]
    UpdateStore2 --> DispatchGoals[Dispatch: setGoals]
    DispatchGoals --> StoreGoals[Store: Update goals list]
    
    StoreGoals --> RenderResults[UI Component: Render Results]
    RenderResults --> DisplayGoals[Display filtered goals]
    DisplayGoals --> ShowBadges[Show active filter badges]
    ShowBadges --> HighlightSearch[Show search term highlighted]
    HighlightSearch --> ShowPagination[Show pagination controls]
    ShowPagination --> ShowCount[Show X results found message]
    ShowCount --> End([END: Results Displayed])

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style End fill:#c8e6c9
    style CacheExists fill:#fff9c4

